fields.name: 20" Paris Bicycle Ages 7+
fields.description:
Condition: The bicycle has been assembled and stripped of its packaging, however it has been used once only due to lack of time to ride it and lack of storage space in a flat.

Collection: As the bicycle has already been assembled, it cannot be shipped; therefore the item can be collected from the following collection point:

Oak Hill Park, 18 Parkside Gardens, London EN4 8JP

Item description: This 20 Inch Paris Bicycle is beautifully designed and tailored to young riders. Whether riding to the park with friends or cycling to the shop, your child is sure to arrive in style with this eye-catching bicycle, making it a perfect celebratory gift.

The elegant steel carrier basket lets kids bring their toys and accessories or other necessities with them wherever they go. It boasts a strong and durable steel frame in bright pink and white with stunning floral details and flowing script. The pink height- adjustable saddle and textured, easy grip handlebars are designed for the rider’s comfort.

Bright pink steel mudguards help to protect your child (and their clothes) from splashes while cycling. The 20 Inch Paris Bike is equipped with a bell and front and rear reflectors to help the cyclist be seen and heard when they’re out and about, guaranteeing their safety. The fixed gear keeps cycling simple, while the front and rear V brakes help to protect the rider. The 20 Inch Paris Bike also features an alloy rim with air pumped tyres, and to top it off, no assembly required! This is truly the perfect bicycle for a child who wants to cycle independently on a bike that looks and rides like a dream.

fields.name: Speed boat RIB 5.0m, 55hp+4hp ou
fields.description:
Speed boat RIB Osprey 5.0m, 55hp Suzuki + 4hp Johnson outboard engines, full water ski and donut gear, complete package, reliable and safe boat
Boat: Osprey RIB (Rigid Inflatable Boat), 5.0metres, A-frame, sports seats, dual fuel tanks, anchor and rope, stow box, watertight bulkhead, non-slip mats
Engine 1: 55hp Suzuki oil injected outboard with electronic ignition, very reliable
Engine 2: 4hp Johnson 2-stroke with pull cord start, very reliable
Trailer: Hallmark Coaster trailer in good condition, with sand wheel (eases beach launches), jockey wheel, high pull winch, light board, new tyres
Skis & Donut: Jobe Allegre skis, Hydroslide Donut, ski rope with boat triangle attachments, Jobe ski jacket, 2 additional life jackets
Radios, compass, tools, cover: Ship to shore VHF radio, hand held VHF radio, off-shore Compass, wheel clamp, tool kit, air-horn, recovery rope, black full boat weather cover for storage, etc etc.
Reason for sale: Young baby restricts boat usage - reluctant sale, will definitely buy another boat in a few years... Great reliable boat, would suit water skiers, leisure boaters and rescue boat usage. This boat and ski pack is ready to go and is great fun.
